      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_03-mhk011.m4a",
      "text": "とにかく、撮影の間はずっと\nこの帽子を被っていて下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Anyway‚ keep wearing this hat\nwhile shooting",
        "id": ""
