      "text": "これ、mihoさんの日よけ帽子じゃ……\nスーツに帽子って、変じゃないですか……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This‚ miho-san's sun hat…\nDoesn't it look strange‚ to have a hat on a suit…?",
        "id": ""
